{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I want to help you re-perceive what philanthropy is,"},{"time":4000,"text":"what it could be,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and what your relationship to it is."},{"time":8000,"text":"And in doing that, I want to offer you a vision,"},{"time":11000,"text":"an imagined future, if you will,"},{"time":14000,"text":"of how, as the poet Seamus Heaney has put it,"},{"time":18000,"text":"\"Once in a lifetime"},{"time":20000,"text":"the longed-for tidal wave of justice can rise up,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and hope and history rhyme.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"I want to start with these word pairs here."},{"time":32000,"text":"We all know which side of these we'd like to be on."},{"time":36000,"text":"When philanthropy was reinvented a century ago,"},{"time":39000,"text":"when the foundation form was actually invented,"},{"time":42000,"text":"they didn't think of themselves on the wrong side of these either."},{"time":46000,"text":"In fact they would never have thought of themselves"},{"time":48000,"text":"as closed and set in their ways,"},{"time":51000,"text":"as slow to respond to new challenges,"},{"time":53000,"text":"as small and risk-averse."},{"time":55000,"text":"And in fact they weren't. They were reinventing charity in those times,"},{"time":58000,"text":"what Rockefeller called \"the business of benevolence.\""},{"time":61000,"text":"But by the end of the 20th century,"},{"time":63000,"text":"a new generation of critics and reformers"},{"time":66000,"text":"had come to see philanthropy just this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70000,"text":"The thing to watch for"},{"time":72000,"text":"as a global philanthropy industry comes about --"},{"time":74000,"text":"and that's exactly what is happening --"},{"time":77000,"text":"is how the aspiration is to flip"},{"time":79000,"text":"these old assumptions,"},{"time":81000,"text":"for philanthropy to become open and big"},{"time":83000,"text":"and fast and connected, in service of the long term."},{"time":86000,"text":"This entrepreneurial energy"},{"time":88000,"text":"is emerging from many quarters."},{"time":90000,"text":"And it's driven and propelled forward by new leaders, like many of the people here,"},{"time":93000,"text":"by new tools, like the ones we've seen here,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and by new pressures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"I've been following this change for quite a while now, and participating in it."},{"time":101000,"text":"This report is our main public report."},{"time":103000,"text":"What it tells is the story of how today"},{"time":105000,"text":"actually could be as historic"},{"time":107000,"text":"as 100 years ago."},{"time":109000,"text":"What I want to do is share some of the coolest things"},{"time":112000,"text":"that are going on with you."},{"time":114000,"text":"And as I do that, I'm not going to dwell much"},{"time":117000,"text":"on the very large philanthropy that everybody already knows about --"},{"time":121000,"text":"the Gates or the Soros or the Google."},{"time":124000,"text":"Instead, what I want to do"},{"time":127000,"text":"is talk about the philanthropy of all of us:"},{"time":131000,"text":"the democratization of philanthropy."},{"time":133000,"text":"This is a moment in history when the average person"},{"time":135000,"text":"has more power than at any time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"What I'm going to do is look at five categories of experiments,"},{"time":141000,"text":"each of which challenges an old assumption of philanthropy."},{"time":146000,"text":"The first is mass collaboration, represented here by Wikipedia."},{"time":150000,"text":"Now, this may surprise you."},{"time":152000,"text":"But remember, philanthropy is about giving of time and talent, not just money."},{"time":157000,"text":"Clay Shirky, that great chronicler of everything networked,"},{"time":161000,"text":"has captured the assumption that this challenges"},{"time":163000,"text":"in such a beautiful way."},{"time":165000,"text":"He said, \"We have lived in this world"},{"time":167000,"text":"where little things are done for love"},{"time":169000,"text":"and big things for money."},{"time":171000,"text":"Now we have Wikipedia."},{"time":173000,"text":"Suddenly big things can be done for love.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"Watch, this spring, for Paul Hawken's new book --"},{"time":180000,"text":"Author and entrepreneur many of you may know about."},{"time":182000,"text":"The book is called \"Blessed Unrest.\""},{"time":184000,"text":"And when it comes out, a series of wiki sites"},{"time":186000,"text":"under the label WISER, are going to launch at the same time."},{"time":189000,"text":"WISER stands for World Index"},{"time":191000,"text":"for Social and Environmental Responsibility."},{"time":194000,"text":"WISER sets out to document, link and empower"},{"time":196000,"text":"what Paul calls the largest movement,"},{"time":199000,"text":"and fastest-growing movement in human history:"},{"time":201000,"text":"humanity's collective immune response"},{"time":204000,"text":"to today's threats."},{"time":206000,"text":"Now, all of these big things for love -- experiments --"},{"time":210000,"text":"aren't going to take off."},{"time":212000,"text":"But the ones that do"},{"time":214000,"text":"are going to be the biggest, the most open,"},{"time":216000,"text":"the fastest, the most connected form of philanthropy in human history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Second category is online philanthropy marketplaces."},{"time":223000,"text":"This is, of course, to philanthropy"},{"time":225000,"text":"what eBay and Amazon are to commerce."},{"time":229000,"text":"Think of it as peer-to-peer philanthropy."},{"time":232000,"text":"And this challenges yet another assumption,"},{"time":235000,"text":"which is that organized philanthropy is only for the very wealthy."},{"time":239000,"text":"Take a look, if you haven't, at DonorsChoose."},{"time":242000,"text":"Omidyar Network has made a big investment in DonorsChoose."},{"time":245000,"text":"It's one of the best known of these new marketplaces"},{"time":247000,"text":"where a donor can go straight into a classroom"},{"time":249000,"text":"and connect with what a teacher says they need."},{"time":252000,"text":"Take a look at Changing the Present,"},{"time":254000,"text":"started by a TEDster, next time you need a wedding present or a holiday present."},{"time":257000,"text":"GiveIndia is for a whole country."},{"time":259000,"text":"And it goes on and on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261000,"text":"The third category is represented by Warren Buffet,"},{"time":264000,"text":"which I call aggregated giving."},{"time":266000,"text":"It's not just that Warren Buffet was so amazingly generous"},{"time":269000,"text":"in that historic act last summer."},{"time":271000,"text":"It's that he challenged another assumption,"},{"time":273000,"text":"that every giver should have his or her own"},{"time":275000,"text":"fund or foundation."},{"time":277000,"text":"There are now, today, so many new funds"},{"time":281000,"text":"that are aggregating giving and investing,"},{"time":283000,"text":"bringing together people"},{"time":286000,"text":"around a common goal, to think bigger."},{"time":288000,"text":"One of the best known is Acumen Fund, led by Jacqueline Novogratz,"},{"time":292000,"text":"a TEDster who got a big boost here at TED."},{"time":294000,"text":"But there are many others: New Profit in Cambridge,"},{"time":297000,"text":"New School's Venture Fund in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":300000,"text":"Venture Philanthropy Partners in Washington,"},{"time":303000,"text":"Global Fund for Women in San Francisco."},{"time":305000,"text":"Take a look at these."},{"time":307000,"text":"These funds are to philanthropy"},{"time":310000,"text":"what venture capital, private equity, and eventually mutual funds"},{"time":315000,"text":"are to investing,"},{"time":317000,"text":"but with a twist --"},{"time":319000,"text":"because often a community forms around these funds,"},{"time":324000,"text":"as it has at Acumen and other places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"Now, imagine for a second"},{"time":330000,"text":"these first three types of experiments:"},{"time":333000,"text":"mass collaboration, online marketplaces, aggregated giving."},{"time":336000,"text":"And understand how they help us re-perceive"},{"time":339000,"text":"what organized philanthropy is."},{"time":341000,"text":"It's not about foundations necessarily; it's about the rest of us."},{"time":344000,"text":"And imagine the mash-up, if you will, of these things, in the future,"},{"time":349000,"text":"when these things come together in the experiments of the future --"},{"time":351000,"text":"imagine that somebody puts up, say,"},{"time":354000,"text":"100 million dollars"},{"time":356000,"text":"for an inspiring goal --"},{"time":358000,"text":"there were 21 gifts of 100 million dollars or more in the US last year,"},{"time":361000,"text":"not out of the question --"},{"time":364000,"text":"but only puts it up if it's matched"},{"time":367000,"text":"by millions of small gifts from around the globe,"},{"time":370000,"text":"thereby engaging lots of people,"},{"time":372000,"text":"and building visibility and engaging people"},{"time":374000,"text":"in the goal that's stated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"I'm going to look quickly at the fourth and fifth categories,"},{"time":379000,"text":"which are innovation, competitions and social investing."},{"time":383000,"text":"They're betting a visible competition, a prize,"},{"time":387000,"text":"can attract talent and money to some of the most difficult issues,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and thereby speed the solution."},{"time":393000,"text":"This tackles yet another assumption,"},{"time":396000,"text":"that the giver and the organization is at the center,"},{"time":398000,"text":"as opposed to putting the problem at the center."},{"time":401000,"text":"You can look to these innovators"},{"time":403000,"text":"to help us especially with things that require"},{"time":406000,"text":"technological or scientific solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"That leaves the final category, social investing,"},{"time":414000,"text":"which is really, anyway, the biggest of them all,"},{"time":416000,"text":"represented here by Xigi.net."},{"time":419000,"text":"And this, of course, tackles the biggest assumption of all,"},{"time":423000,"text":"that business is business,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and philanthropy is the vehicle of people who want to create change in the world."},{"time":429000,"text":"Xigi is a new community site"},{"time":431000,"text":"that's built by the community,"},{"time":433000,"text":"linking and mapping this new social capital market."},{"time":437000,"text":"It lists already 1,000 entities"},{"time":439000,"text":"that are offering debt and equity for social enterprise."},{"time":443000,"text":"So we can look to these innovators"},{"time":446000,"text":"to help us remember"},{"time":450000,"text":"that if we can leverage even a small amount of the capital"},{"time":453000,"text":"that seeks a return,"},{"time":455000,"text":"the good that can be driven could be astonishing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460000,"text":"Now, what's really interesting here"},{"time":462000,"text":"is that we're not thinking our way"},{"time":466000,"text":"into a new way of acting;"},{"time":468000,"text":"we're acting our way into a new way of thinking."},{"time":471000,"text":"Philanthropy is reorganizing itself"},{"time":474000,"text":"before our very eyes."},{"time":476000,"text":"And even though all of the experiments and all of the big givers"},{"time":480000,"text":"don't yet fulfill this aspiration,"},{"time":483000,"text":"I think this is the new zeitgeist:"},{"time":485000,"text":"open, big, fast, connected,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and, let us also hope, long."},{"time":490000,"text":"We have got to realize that it is going to take a long time to do these things."},{"time":494000,"text":"If we don't develop the stamina to stick with things --"},{"time":497000,"text":"whatever it is you pick, stick with it --"},{"time":500000,"text":"all of this stuff is just going to be, you know, a fad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"But I'm really hopeful."},{"time":506000,"text":"And I'm hopeful because it's not only philanthropy"},{"time":508000,"text":"that's reorganizing itself,"},{"time":510000,"text":"it's also whole other portions of the social sector,"},{"time":513000,"text":"and of business,"},{"time":516000,"text":"that are busy challenging \"business as usual.\""},{"time":519000,"text":"And everywhere I go, including here at TED,"},{"time":522000,"text":"I feel that there is a new moral hunger"},{"time":526000,"text":"that is growing."},{"time":528000,"text":"What we're seeing is people really wrestling"},{"time":530000,"text":"to describe what is this new thing that's happening."},{"time":533000,"text":"Words like \"philanthrocapitalism,\""},{"time":535000,"text":"and \"natural capitalism,\" and \"philanthroentrepreneur,\""},{"time":537000,"text":"and \"venture philanthropy.\""},{"time":539000,"text":"We don't have a language for it yet."},{"time":541000,"text":"Whatever we call it,"},{"time":543000,"text":"it's new, it's beginning,"},{"time":545000,"text":"and I think it's gong to quite significant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549000,"text":"And that's where my imagined future comes in,"},{"time":551000,"text":"which I am going to call the social singularity."},{"time":555000,"text":"Many of you will realize that I'm ripping a bit off of the science fiction writer"},{"time":558000,"text":"Vernor Vinge's notion of a technological singularity,"},{"time":561000,"text":"where a number of trends accelerate and converge"},{"time":563000,"text":"and come together to create, really, a shockingly new reality."},{"time":567000,"text":"It may be that the social singularity"},{"time":570000,"text":"ahead is the one that we fear the most:"},{"time":574000,"text":"a convergence of catastrophes,"},{"time":576000,"text":"of environmental degradation,"},{"time":578000,"text":"of weapons of mass destruction, of pandemics,"},{"time":580000,"text":"of poverty."},{"time":582000,"text":"That's because"},{"time":584000,"text":"our ability to confront the problems that we face"},{"time":588000,"text":"has not kept pace with our ability to create them."},{"time":591000,"text":"And as we've heard here,"},{"time":593000,"text":"it is no exaggeration to say"},{"time":595000,"text":"that we hold the future of our civilization in our hands"},{"time":598000,"text":"as never before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"The question is, is there a positive social singularity?"},{"time":604000,"text":"Is there a frontier for us"},{"time":606000,"text":"of how we live together?"},{"time":609000,"text":"Our future doesn't have to be imagined."},{"time":611000,"text":"We can create a future where hope and history rhyme."},{"time":616000,"text":"But we have a problem."},{"time":618000,"text":"Our experience to date, both individually and collectively,"},{"time":622000,"text":"hasn't prepared us for what we're going to need to do,"},{"time":625000,"text":"or who we're going to need to be."},{"time":628000,"text":"We are going to need"},{"time":630000,"text":"a new generation of citizen leaders"},{"time":635000,"text":"willing to commit ourselves to growing and changing and learning"},{"time":638000,"text":"as rapidly as possible."},{"time":640000,"text":"That's why I have one last thing I want to show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"This is a photograph taken about 100 years ago"},{"time":645000,"text":"of my grandfather and great-grandfather."},{"time":648000,"text":"This is a newspaper publisher and a banker."},{"time":651000,"text":"And they were great community leaders."},{"time":653000,"text":"And, yes, they were great philanthropists."},{"time":656000,"text":"I keep this photograph close by to me --"},{"time":658000,"text":"it's in my office --"},{"time":660000,"text":"because I've always felt a mystical connection to these two men,"},{"time":663000,"text":"both of whom I never knew."},{"time":666000,"text":"And so, in their honor,"},{"time":670000,"text":"I want to offer you this blank slide."},{"time":675000,"text":"And I want you to imagine"},{"time":678000,"text":"that this a photograph of you."},{"time":681000,"text":"And I want you to think about the community"},{"time":684000,"text":"that you want to be part of creating."},{"time":686000,"text":"Whatever that means to you."},{"time":689000,"text":"And I want you to imagine"},{"time":692000,"text":"that it's 100 years from now,"},{"time":695000,"text":"and your grandchild, or great-grandchild,"},{"time":699000,"text":"or niece or nephew or god-child,"},{"time":703000,"text":"is looking at this photograph of you."},{"time":707000,"text":"What is the story you most want for them to tell?"},{"time":721000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":723000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}